title: Marianne Vos Untouchable with Huge Sprint Win at La Vuelta Femenina
content:
Overnight race leader Blanka Vas holds on to maillot rojo by just one second, Vos moves up to second overall with her 252nd career win.

Read the full article at Marianne Vos Untouchable with Huge Sprint Win at La Vuelta Femenina on Velo.
author: Jim Cotton
